title: Grateful Dead Live at Carrier Dome, Syracuse U on 1984-10-20
lineage: Transfer: Master Cassette > Nakamichi CR7a playback with no dolby> Korg mr2000 (1 bit, 5.6 Mhz). Render from 1 bit to 24 48 wave file using AudioGate.  Pre dolby nr decode eq & software dolby B decode using Nuendo & DDICodec.

Bertha >

Comment

Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
